data.title: Commercial, Industrial, Municipal Building Contractor
data.meta_description: Summit Construction is a licensed Florida General Contractor providing construction management, renovations, electrical, design-build, estimating and other GC services to municipal, commercial and industrial customers.
data.meta_site_name: Vero Beach, Florida General Contractor | Commercial, Industrial, Municipal Building Contractor | South Florida, St. Lucie, Indian River
data.text:
Summit Construction of Vero Beach, LLC was established in 1999 with one thing in mind—provide high-quality, on-time construction management and contracting services for our community. Summit was founded by Brad Schuh who serves as President and Project Manager for all projects. We are a state certified General Contractor that specializes in providing bonded construction management and general contracting services in Indian River, St. Lucie, Okeechobee and Brevard Counties. The members of Summit have been providing these services for over 25 years. We have been involved with countless projects in this area and have gained a tremendous wealth of experience, while building an impressive list of clients. Many of the projects in our portfolio were awarded from repeat clients. We believe that this is a testament to our quality workmanship and ability to create a partnership with our clients. Repeat clients mean one thing—we must be doing it right.

We take great pride in the work we do in our home area of Florida—because we become a part of the improvement of our community.
